<li class="item">
  <div class="list">
    <div class="list-image">
      <%= link_to profile_path(permalink:current_user.username), class: "list-photo" do %>
          <img src="images/photo/photo02.jpg" alt="photo" />
          <span class="verify-icon"><i class="spicon spicon-check"></i></span>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="list-content">
      <div class="list-header">
        <div class="list-header-text">
          <div class="timeline-text1">
            <%= link_to shop.name, show_malls_path(name:shop.mall.id, permalink:shop.id) %>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-text2">
            <a href="#">Macbook Pro Retina Display</a>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-text3">
            <a href="#">Lotte Shopping Avenue</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="list-nav list-flip">
          <div class="flip-container">
            <div class="flipper">
              <div class="front">
                <img src="images/product/product02.jpg" alt="product" />
              </div>
              <div class="back">
                <div class="list-action">
                  <a href="#"><i class="spicon spicon-like"></i></a>
                  <a href="#"><i class="spicon spicon-comment"></i></a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="list-comment spicon spicon-quote">
    <h4><a href="profile.html">Takeshi Kaneshiro</a></h4>
    <p>このラップトップは本当に素晴らしいです、私はもうそれなしでは生きすることを想像することはできません</p>
  </div>
</li>